<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Tableau de bord</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="nav-brand">
                <a href="/dashboard"><img src="/img/gsb-logo.webp" alt="Logo GSB" class="logo-nav"></a>
            </div>
            <div class="nav-links">
                <a href="/articles">Articles</a>
                <a href="/categories">Catégories</a>
                <a href="/contacts">Contacts</a>
                <a href="/factures">Factures</a>
                <a href="/devis">Devis</a>
                <a href="/profile">Profil</a>
                <a href="/logout">Déconnexion</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container main-content">
        <h1>Tableau de bord</h1>
        
        <div class="dashboard-grid">
            <div class="dashboard-card">
                <h2><svg class="icon-sm" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="3" y="3" width="7" height="7"></rect><rect x="14" y="3" width="7" height="7"></rect><rect x="14" y="14" width="7" height="7"></rect><rect x="3" y="14" width="7" height="7"></rect></svg> Articles</h2>
                <p>Gérez votre catalogue de produits/services</p>
                <a href="/articles" class="btn btn-primary">Voir les articles</a>
            </div>

            <div class="dashboard-card">
                <h2><svg class="icon-sm" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path></svg> Contacts</h2>
                <p>Gérez vos clients et fournisseurs</p>
                <a href="/contacts" class="btn btn-primary">Voir les contacts</a>
            </div>

            <div class="dashboard-card">
                <h2><svg class="icon-sm" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 2c6.627 0 12 5.373 12 12s-5.373 12-12 12S0 20.627 0 14 5.373 2 12 2" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.1"></path><circle cx="12" cy="9" r="2"></circle><path d="M12 14v4"></path><path d="M8 16h8"></path></svg> Factures</h2>
                <p>Créez et suivez vos factures</p>
                <a href="/factures" class="btn btn-primary">Voir les factures</a>
            </div>

            <div class="dashboard-card">
                <h2><svg class="icon-sm" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"></path><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"></polyline><line x1="12" y1="11" x2="12" y2="17"></line><line x1="9" y1="14" x2="15" y2="14"></line></svg> Devis</h2>
                <p>Créez et gérez vos devis</p>
                <a href="/devis" class="btn btn-primary">Voir les devis</a>
            </div>

            <div class="dashboard-card">
                <h2><svg class="icon-sm" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4"></circle><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2m0 3c1.66 0 3 1.34 3 3s-1.34 3-3 3-3-1.34-3-3 1.34-3 3-3m0 14.2c-2.5 0-4.71-1.28-6-3.22.03-1.99 4-3.08 6-3.08 1.99 0 5.97 1.09 6 3.08-1.29 1.94-3.5 3.22-6 3.22"></path></svg> Mon Profil</h2>
                <p>Gérez vos données personnelles et votre sécurité</p>
                <a href="/profile" class="btn btn-primary">Accéder au profil</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2026 - GSB COMPTABILITE | Express.js + SQLite</p>
    </footer>
